    "description": "扮演“new_user”的角色，一位工程师，肩负着修复机器以逃离未知地点的巨大挑战。你的工具？数字逻辑的基本构建块：互补晶体管。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构建你自己的部件</h2> 从电子元件的基础开始，用互补晶体管创建逻辑门。当你从简单的 NAND 和 NOR 逻辑门进步到能够执行复杂任务的复杂电路时，学习电子设计的艺术。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/6a8bd6d9fb9567706611accfdae39a45.poster.avif?t=1755372580\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/6a8bd6d9fb9567706611accfdae39a45.webm?t=1755372580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/6a8bd6d9fb9567706611accfdae39a45.mp4?t=1755372580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组装它们</h2> 将你的逻辑门组合成更大、更复杂的部件。每一次组装都是一个谜题，不仅需要智慧，还需要创造力、计划和前瞻性。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/6f54d5d7dffb1e802f7239028ed49d56.poster.avif?t=1755372580\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/6f54d5d7dffb1e802f7239028ed49d56.webm?t=1755372580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/6f54d5d7dffb1e802f7239028ed49d56.mp4?t=1755372580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >优化</h2> 为效率和空间优化你的设计，挑战你工程才能的极限。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/b549df69f4476bdf945c4c3c2caab4ef.poster.avif?t=1755372580\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/b549df69f4476bdf945c4c3c2caab4ef.webm?t=1755372580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/b549df69f4476bdf945c4c3c2caab4ef.mp4?t=1755372580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >终端</h2> 所有电子设备似乎都无法运行，而它们是你前进的唯一途径。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/cfbf2edc11a2c728ca23a5ec6f836470.poster.avif?t=1755372580\" width=620 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/cfbf2edc11a2c728ca23a5ec6f836470.webm?t=1755372580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/cfbf2edc11a2c728ca23a5ec6f836470.mp4?t=1755372580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >找到你的出路</h2> 前进到一个陌生的世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033160/extras/00a062ad53720f617b681c188b008eb5.avif?t=1755372580\" width=620 height=302 /></span>",
